Name: Ellen's Namecard
Desc: Get by unlocking Ellen's Mindscape: Overtime-Intolerant.
Desc2:
A card with an apathetic Victoria Housekeeping maid printed on it.
These namecards had to be "carefully" prepared under the watchful gaze of the head maid and a professional attendant. Besides handing these out to clients, some have also been given to classmates stuck in the same group project.
